  <entry>
    <title>一个约瑟夫环问题</title>
    <link href="/2022/01/06/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BA%A6%E7%91%9F%E5%A4%AB%E7%8E%AF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2022/01/06/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BA%A6%E7%91%9F%E5%A4%AB%E7%8E%AF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="消除游戏"><a href="#消除游戏" class="headerlink" title="消除游戏"></a>消除游戏</h1><p>​    前两天刚好看到李永乐的数学趣味视频，讲的就是约瑟夫环问题，恰好leetcode每日一题碰到，于是写篇博客记录一下题解，还是蛮有趣的。</p><p>首先看题(leetcode 390.消除游戏  中等难度)：</p><blockquote><p>列表 arr 由在范围 [1, n] 中的所有整数组成，并按严格递增排序。请你对 arr 应用下述算法：</p><p>​     从左到右，删除第一个数字，然后每隔一个数字删除一个，直到到达列表末尾。<br>​      重复上面的步骤，但这次是从右到左。也就是，删除最右侧的数字，然后剩下的数字每隔一个删除一个。<br>​      不断重复这两步，从左到右和从右到左交替进行，直到只剩下一个数字。<br>给你整数 n ，返回 arr 最后剩下的数字。</p></blockquote><h2 id="解法1"><a href="#解法1" class="headerlink" title="解法1"></a>解法1</h2><p>​    利用两个参数记录当前元素head和步长step，再用一个bool参数left记录扫描方向。</p><p>​    解析可以看国外码友给出的，易懂简单，链接在下。</p><p>​    [a link](<a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/elimination-game/discuss/87119/JAVA%3A-Easiest-solution-O(logN)-with-explanation">JAVA: Easiest solution O(logN) with explanation - LeetCode Discuss</a></p><p>​    直接上代码：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">lastRemaining</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> head = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> step = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">bool</span> left = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//int n = n</span><br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (n &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">//从左边开始移除 or（从右边开始移除，数列总数为奇数）</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (left || n % <span class="hljs-number">2</span> != <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br>                head += step;<br>            &#125;<br>            step &lt;&lt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">//步长 * 2</span><br>            n &gt;&gt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">//总数 / 2</span><br>            left = !left; <span class="hljs-comment">//取反移除方向</span><br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> head;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="解法2（约瑟夫环问题）"><a href="#解法2（约瑟夫环问题）" class="headerlink" title="解法2（约瑟夫环问题）"></a>解法2（约瑟夫环问题）</h2><p>​    不妨定义，f[i]为在连续序列[1,i]中进行<strong>起始从左往右</strong>扫描并轮流间隔删除，最终左边剩下的那个符号，g[i]为在连续序列[1,i]中进行<strong>起始从右往左</strong>扫描并轮流间隔删除，最终右边剩下的那个符号。</p><p>​    所以有： f[i] + g[i] = i+1</p><p>​    同时，在每一轮扫描删除后，我们需要进行<em>重新编号i</em>确保f[i]和g[i]的合法状态，在重新编号后，还需要将答案编号映射回原编号。每一次扫描，新产生序列长度为**i/2(这里采用加粗表示向下取整，下同)**。</p><p>​    可得第二个公式： f[i] = g[<strong>i/2</strong>]*2</p><p>​    连列消除g[i]，得到f[i] = 2 * (<strong>i/2</strong> + 1 - f[<strong>i/2</strong>])</p><p>​    此时很明显需要求的函数lastRemaining就是f[i]，注意递归出口f[1]=1</p><p>​    贴代码：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">lastRemaining</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ? <span class="hljs-number">1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">2</span> * (n / <span class="hljs-number">2</span> + <span class="hljs-number">1</span> - <span class="hljs-built_in">lastRemaining</span>(n / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>    &#125; <br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>算法</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
